column5: Headed up to Lynn Lake soon woundering how far N is there open water right now?
It should be off now or pretty soon. One year it was on Reindeer until the end of the first week in June. Good Luck!
Apilot aquaintance said on last Friday it was open far past the 55th paralell. I would say with the rain it is all open now. Don't worry!Have Fun!
